已测试可用的 API
 1. 地理编码（地址→坐标）
bash
 请求
GET https://restapi.amap.com/v3/geocode/geo?address=北京市朝阳区阜通东大街6号&key=xxx&sig=xxx
 响应
{
  "status": "1",
  "geocodes": {
    "location": "116.482086,39.990496",
    "formattedaddress": "北京市朝阳区阜通东大街6号"
  }
}
 2. 逆地理编码（坐标→地址）
bash
 请求
GET https://restapi.amap.com/v3/geocode/regeo?location=116.482086,39.990496&key=xxx&sig=xxx
 响应
{
  "status": "1",
  "regeocode": {
    "formattedaddress": "北京市朝阳区望京街道方恒国际中心"
  }
}
 3. 天气预报
bash
 请求（城市编码，如110105=北京朝阳）
GET https://restapi.amap.com/v3/weather/weatherInfo?city=110105&key=xxx&sig=xxx
 响应
{
  "lives": {
    "city": "朝阳区",
    "weather": "阴",
    "temperature": "16",
    "windpower": "≤3"
  }
}
 4. POI 搜索
bash
 请求
GET https://restapi.amap.com/v3/place/text?keywords=医院&city=110105&key=xxx&sig=xxx
 响应
{
  "pois": {
    "name": "首都医科大学附属北京安贞医院",
    "address": "安贞路2号",
    "location": "116.407394,39.971253"
  }
}
